name: Uleen%27Arael
content: Uleen'Arael was a Rutian Twi'lek female bounty hunter who was active during the reign of the Galactic Empire. Between 3 ABY and 4 ABY, Lady Domina Tagge of the House of Tagge placed a bounty on rogue archaeologist Doctor Chelli Lona Aphra which Uleen'Arael attempted to collect alongside fellow hunter Jepha. The pair traveled to Arveesh Station where they encountered Aphra, though their attempt to capture the doctor was thwarted when Wookiee bounty hunter Krrsantan stood in the way of Jepha's shot. In response, Uleen'Arael told Jepha to go through the Wookiee and to be quick as the Hal'Lath Quadruplets had arrived and would want to collect the bounty. Jepha then fired stun shots at Krrsantan, which enraged the Wookiee and in retaliation he attacked Uleen'Arael and Jepha. This allowed Aphra to make her escape, though she was eventually captured by Just Lucky and Kharrek.
